This paper deals with a machine learning problem of ordinal regression, which involves predicting an ordered set of classes. The paper proposes a novel transductive learning paradigm for ordinal regression, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper discusses the use of loss functions and label swapping schemes, which are commonly used in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as these sub-categories are also relevant to the topics discussed in the paper.
